nk\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kelly Slater\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Slater\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Slater\"}, {\"begin\": 1695, \"end\": 1697, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Central_Time_Zone\", \"score\": 0.8531092712187961, \"rank\": 0.10767358038618097, \"text\": \"CT\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Central_Time_Zone\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Central_Time_Zone\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the scene\", \"from\": 1442, \"to\": 1451}, {\"ngram\": \"his new wave pool\", \"from\": 1455, \"to\": 1472}, {\"ngram\": \"Abu Dhabi\", \"from\": 1476, \"to\": 1485}, {\"ngram\": \"Credit\", \"from\": 1486, \"to\": 1492}, {\"ngram\": \"a major stake\", \"from\": 1538, \"to\": 1551}, {\"ngram\": \"Slater's newly opened man-made wave\", \"from\": 1606, \"to\": 1641}, {\"ngram\": \"Surf Abu Dhabi\", \"from\": 1645, \"to\": 1659}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The obvious attraction of wave pool events is guaranteed quality waves for competition and proximity for spectators, though Robinson echoed criticism of previous Surf Ranch events that led to several high-profile withdrawals from the 2021 edition.\", \"from\": 1716, \"to\": 1963, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1840, \"end\": 1848, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Robinson\", \"score\": 0.9925931041234872, \"rank\": 0.005568212866819815, \"text\": \"Robinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Robinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Robinson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The obvious attraction\", \"from\": 1716, \"to\": 1738}, {\"ngram\": \"wave pool events\", \"from\": 1742, \"to\": 1758}, {\"ngram\": \"quality waves\", \"from\": 1773, \"to\": 1786}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 1791, \"to\": 1802}, {\"ngram\": \"proximity\", \"from\": 1807, \"to\": 1816}, {\"ngram\": \"spectators\", \"from\": 1821, \"to\": 1831}, {\"ngram\": \"criticism\", \"from\": 1856, \"to\": 1865}, {\"ngram\": \"previous Surf Ranch events\", \"from\": 1869, \"to\": 1895}, {\"ngram\": \"several high-profile withdrawals\", \"from\": 1908, \"to\": 1940}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2021 edition\", \"from\": 1946, \"to\": 1962}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Personally, if a [Olympic] host country has waves, then use them.\", \"from\": 1965, \"to\": 2031, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a [Olympic] host country\", \"from\": 1981, \"to\": 2005}, {\"ngram\": \"waves\", \"from\": 2010, \"to\": 2015}]}, {\"sentence\": \"America has waves in Hawaii and California,\\\" Robinson told this masthead.\", \"from\": 2032, \"to\": 2105, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2053, \"end\": 2059, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hawaii\", \"score\": 0.9999999856986507, \"rank\": 1.4300320646696538e-08, \"text\": \"Hawaii\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hawaii\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hawaii\"}, {\"begin\": 2064, \"end\": 2074, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\", \"score\": 0.9999999999954525, \"rank\": 2.929355421122275e-12, \"text\": \"California\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\"}, {\"begin\": 2077, \"end\": 2085, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Robinson\", \"score\": 0.9925931041234872, \"rank\": 0.005568212866819815, \"text\": \"Robinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Robinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Robinson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"America\", \"from\": 2032, \"to\": 2039}, {\"ngram\": \"waves\", \"from\": 2044, \"to\": 2049}, {\"ngram\": \"this masthead\", \"from\": 2091, \"to\": 2104}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Some people might prefer a wave pool because it suits their surfing but to me, working out the ocean is a big part of competitive surfing.\", \"from\": 2107, \"to\": 2246, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Some people\", \"from\": 2108, \"to\": 2119}, {\"ngram\": \"a wave pool\", \"from\": 2133, \"to\": 2144}, {\"ngram\": \"their surfing\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2175}, {\"ngram\": \"the ocean\", \"from\": 2199, \"to\": 2208}, {\"ngram\": \"a big part\", \"from\": 2212, \"to\": 2222}, {\"ngram\": \"competitive surfing\", \"from\": 2226, \"to\": 2245}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's such a skill and you take that away in a wave pool.\", \"from\": 2247, \"to\": 2303, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"such a skill\", \"from\": 2252, \"to\": 2264}, {\"ngram\": \"a wave pool\", \"from\": 2291, \"to\": 2302}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kelly Slater's new wave pool in Abu Dhabi.Credit:YouTube \\\"And from a spectator point of view, personally I do not think wave pools are great to watch.\", \"from\": 2305, \"to\": 2456, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2305, \"end\": 2317, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Slater\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kelly Slater\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Slater\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Slater\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Abu Dhabi\", \"from\": 2337, \"to\": 2346}, {\"ngram\": \"a spectator point\", \"from\": 2372, \"to\": 2389}, {\"ngram\": \"view\", \"from\": 2393, \"to\": 2397}, {\"ngram\": \"wave pools\", \"from\": 2425, \"to\": 2435}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Maybe one day they will be.\", \"from\": 2457, \"to\": 2484, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But right now, I think it's very repetitive to watch.\", \"from\": 2485, \"to\": 2538, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mostly the waves can only handle so much size and if a wave's quite long it gets boring, it's the same manoeuvres and moves over and over again.\", \"from\": 2539, \"t